# erawan-cluster

REST API written in Go for:
- HAProxy tenant config generation + reload.
- MySQL InnoDB Cluster lifecycle automation through Ansible playbooks.

## Table of Contents
- [Tech Stack](#tech-stack)
- [Project Structure](#project-structure)
- [How It Works](#how-it-works)
- [Prerequisites](#prerequisites)
- [Install](#install)
- [Run](#run)
